      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WICKED VICTREE (2) broke in the run and finished a distant seventh on debut last start over 1850m at Marburg. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. This doesn't look as hard so he can bounce back. FREE DELIVERY (9) finished fifth last start, beaten 12 metres at this track over 1780m. Capable of playing a major role so has to be respected. OUR ULTIMATE BEATY (4) good effort to finish in the money two back then suffered interference and broke last start but still managed to finish third, beaten 19 metres, over 1850m at Marburg. This doesn't look as hard so she is right in the mix again. ARKANSAURUS (8) is stepping out for the first time. By Mcwicked and hails from the Grant Dixon stable. Finds a nice race so anticipating a bright start to her career.",
